hadiths.en:
Ghiyath ibn Ibrahim narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al -Sadiq {a.s} 
from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al -Baqir {a.s}, that Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib {a.s} 
disliked the sale of meat in exchange for live animals.  
[REFERENCES] Man La Yahduruhu Al-Faqih, Vol.3 p.278 • Wasa’il Al-Shi’ah, Vol.18 p.143 
﴿HADITH ﴾
